rows.label: tlk70000120_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hail, and well met!
I'm Elba, the gallant Gulan knight!
At your service!

rows.label: tlk70000120_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Now, take a look at this weapon!
The chief recently gifted it me!

rows.label: tlk70000120_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Did you know? If you keep using the
weapon, eventually your skills with that
weapon will grow! That's important!

rows.label: tlk70000120_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Just you wait! I'm going to take such
good care of this and train like the
clappers, and soon I'll be a true knight!
